    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for someone prioritizing functionality over aesthetics. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some wear and staining, though all essential electronics and mechanical components are in working order. It has been regularly serviced and is ready for daily use, making it a practical choice for a budget-conscious buyer.",
