      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though you should expect the typical cosmetic wear associated with its age, including several noticeable scratches on the exterior and some minor dings on the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery shows some fading and signs of use, but the cabin remains clean and functional. It has been well-maintained mechanically, making it a solid choice for someone who prioritizes performance over a perfect aesthetic.",
