    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-state condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance that is truly uncompromising. Every surface and mechanical component adheres to the highest aesthetic and functional benchmarks. An exceptional opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
