      "description": "We are pleased to present an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle is offered in pristine, showroom condition, having been curated with exhaustive attention to detail and mechanical excellence. It features flawless coachwork and an interior that retains its original factory luster. For the discerning buyer who demands excellence without compromise, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a benchmark-quality vehicle of the highest order.",
      "price": 46500.0,
